column1: #List of all subunit/gene pairs and their relevant properties

column8: Assembly order (1 - A assembles first; -1 - B assembles first; 0 - A + B assemble simultaneously or in parallel)
column9: Evidence of gene fusion (1 - yes; 0 - no)
column10: Assembly pathway would be conserved upon fusion (1 - yes; 0 - no; blank - either no evidence of fusion or it's a heterodimer
column11: Abundance of subunit A considering data from all organims
column12: Abundance of subunit B considering data from all organisms
column13: Abundance of subunit A considering data from E. coli only
column14: Abundance of subunit B considering data from E. coli only
column16: Position of Gene A in operon
column17: Position of Gene B in operon
column18: Gene order conservation for adjacent pairs (C - completely conserved; M - mostly conserved with <4 deviations across all organisms; N - not conserved; L - evolutionarily limited with <5 examples in just one phylogenetic branch)
